pulltitle: Add MCCs for Armenia, Martinique and the Democratic Republic of Congo (bug 1227631)
pullsbody:
https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1227631

MCC 340 could be Guadeloupe, Martinique or Saint-Martin. We don't support this kind
of configuration yet, moving that mcc to Martinique because that's coherent with how
we generate things with `mobile_codes` library.
pull_repo_desc: Common, universal constants for the Firefox Marketplace
pull_commit_message:
Add MCCs for Armenia, Martinique and the Democratic Republic of Congo (bug 1227631)

MCC 340 could be Guadeloupe, Martinique or Saint-Martin. We don't support this kind
of configuration yet, moving that mcc to Martinique because that's coherent with how
we generate things with mobile_codes library.

Fix region adolescence (bug 1058257)

All regions added in 157e3942 were set to adolescent: False by mistake.

pullsbody:
https://bugzilla.mozilla.org/show_bug.cgi?id=1058257

Some notes:
- No distinction is made between independant countries and dependent territories. We're just pulling the data from ISO 3166.
- `regions.js` still exports REGION_CHOICES_SLUGS for the moment, but no longer translates them, to reduce the number of translations needed in frontend projects (which would increase size significantly)
- `regions.styl` is going to generate enormous css files. It might be better to avoid it and directly link to the image in HTML.
- `default_currency` is removed everywhere
pull_repo_desc: Common, universal constants for the Firefox Marketplace
pull_commit_message:
All all countries. (bug 1058257)

Some notes:
- No distinction is made between independant countries and dependent
  territories. We're just pulling the data from ISO 3166.
- regions.js still exports REGION_CHOICES_SLUGS for the moment, but
  no longer translates them, to reduce the number of translations
  needed in frontend projects (which would increase size significantly)
- regions.styl is going to generate enormous css files. It might
  be better to avoid it and directly link to the image in HTML.
- default_currency is removed everywhere
